OL,3,CPolice investigating after Kidwelly
OL,4,Chouse fire forces locals to evacuate
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a house
OL,7,Ffire in a Carmarthenshire town forced
OL,8,Flocals to evacuate their homes for
OL,9,Fseveral days.
OL,11,FThe fire was reported on Lady Street
OL,12,Fin Kidwelly at around 4.20am on
OL,13,FTuesday 24 March.
OL,15,FDyfed Powys Police said all residents
OL,16,Freturned home on Friday evening after
OL,17,Fthe affected building was made safe.
OL,19,FThe road remains closed while further
OL,20,Fwork is carried out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
