OL,3,CPolice investigating after Kidwelly
OL,4,Chouse fire forces locals to evacuate
OL,6,FWhile officers are no longer at the
OL,7,Fproperty, an investigation to
OL,8,Fdetermine the cause of the fire
OL,9,Fcontinues.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the force said:
OL,12,F"We'd like to thank residents and the
OL,13,Fwider community for their patience
OL,14,Fwhile the necessary enquiries were
OL,15,Fcarried out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
