OL,3,CPolice investigating after Kidwelly
OL,4,Chouse fire forces locals to evacuate
OL,6,F"We ask any witnesses, or anyone who
OL,7,Fmay have any information about the
OL,8,Fcause of the fire, to get in touch. We
OL,9,Fwould also like to hear from anyone
OL,10,Fwith CCTV, doorbell or dashcam footage
OL,11,Ffrom between 11pm on Monday (23/3) and
OL,12,F4am on (24/3)."
